name: Birthdayscript
tagline: This script is helpful in automatically commenting "thank you" messages for your friend's wall-posts on your Facebook wall on your birth day.

BirthDayScript
==============

This script is helpful in automatically commenting "thank you" messages for your friend's wall-posts on your birth day.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
